<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5> dot one’s i’s and cross one’s t’s • mind one’s p’s and q’s</xh5><p> <i>dot one’s i’s and cross one’s t’s</i>—(also: dot the i’s and cross the t’s) be very thorough; pay attention to small details: When you do an investigation of somebody very prominent, make sure you <u>dot your i’s and cross your t’s</u>.</p><p> <i>mind one’s p’s and q’s—</i>be careful of one’s actions and behavior; act and speak correctly: You’ll have to <u>mind your p’s and q’s</u> if you want to be invited there again.</p> </entry>
